Class LogEntry

java.lang.Object
LogEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<LogEntry>
public class LogEntry extends Object implements Comparable<LogEntry>
Store the data from a single line of a web-server log file. Individual fields are made available via accessors such as getHour() and getMinute().
Version:
2024.03.18
Author:
Andrew Steidle
